A Customer Billing  System, which will manage all the required activities in a hotel such as entering a customerâ€™s name, address, bed room type, calculating total bill amount, showing tax value and displaying it on a text screen.
The application consists of 3 buttons-
1. Total (calculates total bill amount)
2. Reset (Resets all the entry)
3. Exit (prompts a messagebox for confirmation to exit the application)

Python interface named Tkinter is used for making GUI(graphical user interface).
